The netCDF operators NCO version 2.8.7 are ready. 

http://nco.sf.net (Homepage)
http://dust.ess.uci.edu/nco (Homepage "mirror")

This is a double-paper bag release to correct a recently introduced
bug that caused ncap packing to fail and Cygwin builds to fail.

Enjoy,
Charlie

Bug-fixes:
1. ncap packing works again (broken in 2.8.4)
2. Default GCC builds (without --enable-*-custom) work again (broken in 2.8.6)

Feature changes:
1. None

Other user-visible changes:
1. None

User-invisible changes:
1. None
